         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">6th August 1857 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your letter of the 27th Ultimo, ¶  and referring to the subject thereof to inform you, that there is no objection to your obt...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.08.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 57/2388, unit 3, p. 389, VPRS 975/P1 outward registered correspondence, VA 669 Public Works Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation by unknown: 'Smith Adamson &amp; Co £31.15.6. | Smith Adamson &amp; Co 3.3.— | J. J. Rule 13.9.6 | <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">£48.8.0</hi>
                     </seg>'.</p>
               </note>6th August 1857</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your letter of the 27th Ultimo,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M to D. Moore, 27 July 1857.</p>
               </note> and referring to the subject thereof to inform you, that there is no objection to your obtaining the plants &amp;c which you recommend for purchase, keeping in view the fact that the balance remaining of the vote to cover the cost thereof is only £49 —</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">(Signed) T. C. Balmain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For C.P.W.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Commissioner of Public Works.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Muëller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Govt Botanist</p>
